I tried to explain in that last paragraph about how he's starting to think and wonder about life. He's never had to do this, so alot of philosophical questions are hitting him like a brick wall. Which are making him weak at what he's best at being, a soldier.<br>
He has to accept these feels before he'll become a true person. His inner demons still plague him. <p><B>Koz. Lean, Mean, Posting machine.</B>
