He will go back and forth as one side of his personality dominates according to what's appropriate to the situation. Xvar knows that that day is going to be a hard one and one of long traveling, possibily fighting. This makes him switch gears to what seems more logical, the fighting mindset.<br>
Try and think about it a little Vija, Xvar is dealing with normal emotions he's never had to deal with, this does sometimes negative things to a personality. And his own confusion is apparent in how he switches moods.  <p><B>Koz. Lean, Mean, Posting machine.</B>
